{
  "page": "Plaza of Punishment",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>Plaza of Punishment</b> is a plaza in <a href=\"/index.php/Astapor\" title=\"Astapor\">Astapor</a>. It is where new slaves taken into Astapor are first brought, so they can see slaves who have been punished or executed.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> It is larger than the <a href=\"/index.php/Plaza_of_Pride\" title=\"Plaza of Pride\">Plaza of Pride</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Plaza_of_Punishment&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Plaza_of_Punishment&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>During the <a href=\"/index.php/Siege_of_Astapor\" title=\"Siege of Astapor\">siege of Astapor</a>, after the faux <a href=\"/index.php/Unsullied\" title=\"Unsullied\">Unsullied</a> of the late King <a href=\"/index.php/Cleon\" title=\"Cleon\">Cleon</a> are defeated in their sortie against the <a href=\"/index.php/Yunkai\" title=\"Yunkai\">Yunkai'i</a> and their allies, the <a href=\"/index.php/Green_Grace_(Astapor)\" title=\"Green Grace (Astapor)\">Green Grace</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Astapor\" title=\"Astapor\">Astapor</a> is impaled in the Plaza of Punishment and left to die.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Plaza_of_Punishment&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_27\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 27\">Chapter 27</a>, Daenerys III.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_30\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 30\">Chapter 30</a>, Daenerys V.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403114943\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.011 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.012 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 203/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8582/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 753/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 44/2097152 byte